column2: SELECT up_id, dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) as objId FROM #upload WHERE dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) IS NOT NULL EXEC spExecuteSQL &&&'&&&+ cast(x.objId as varchar(#)) + &&&&&& as objID, p.ra, p.dec, p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field, dbo.fPhotoTypeN(p.type) as type, s.z, s.z_warning e.Flux_Hb_#, e.Flux_Hb_#_Err e.Flux_Ha_#, e.Flux_Ha_#_Err FROM #upload u JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id JOIN PhotoTag p ON p.objID = x.objID JOIN PhotoObjAll ph ON ph.objID = x.objID JOIN galSpecInfo s ON s.specObjID = ph.specObjID JOIN emissionLinesPort a ON e.specObjID = ph.specObjID WHERE p.type =# ORDER BY x.up_id &&&#', @log=#, @filter=#
